<s> Subject: feature string for Load-Save  </s>
<s> Fixed. "LS-Load" for the DOMBuilder and "LS-Save" for the DOMWriter.  </s>
<s> Synchronous mode is always required.  </s>
<s> Asynchronous mode is required if you support "LS-Load-Async".  </s>
<s> Not sure what to do with the DocumentLS interface yet.  </s>
<s> more to come on that in the future.  </s>
