<s> Is there a feature string for testing the various DOM3 DocumentAS interface?  </s>
<s> The spec says " One feature string for the AS-editing interfaces listed in this section is "AS-EDIT" and another feature string for document-editing interfaces is "AS-DOC"."  </s>
<s> However, neither of these obviously applies to the DocumentAS interface which falls under the heading "Validation and Other Interfaces."  </s>
<s> Elliotte Rusty Harold | elharo@metalab.unc.edu | Writer/Programmer | The XML Bible, 2nd Edition (Hungry Minds, 2001) | Read Cafe au Lait for Java news: http://www.cafeaulait.org/  </s>
<s> | Read Cafe con Leche for XML news: http://www.ibiblio.org/xml/  </s>
<s> |  </s>
<s> Since the functionality under "Validation and Other Interfaces" is common to both AS-editing and document-editing, a retrieval of either "AS-EDIT" or "AS-DOC" could be interpreted as having support of these features.  </s>
<s> However, if document-editing is to be completely independent of AS-editing, then perhaps another feature string should be made for functionality under this section.  </s>
<s> We will discuss in our AS ET telcon.  </s>
